name: Kalamint
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Kalamint, a leader of the Clean NFT movement is built on Tezos, an LPoS blockchain. It is backed by Draper Goren Holm Ventures, Amesten Capital and others and is one of the only NFT marketplaces which is truly on-chain, meaning that the data on the chain can never be altered or lost.
